  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>The word <code>motivate</code> is a verb that means to give someone a reason to act in a certain way.</p>\n<p>By adding <code>-ed</code> to the end, it becomes <code>motivated</code>, an adjective that describes someone who has been influenced or encouraged to do something. For example:\n<code>I'm not motivated to work late today</code></p>\n<p>This sentence means the person does not feel like they want to work extra hours today. <code>Not motivated</code> means they don't have the energy or desire to do it.</p>\n</section>",
